javax.accessibility.Accessible, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable
public class ManageRecordButtonPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel

Provides buttons for the user to interact with the record. Allows the user to add a new record, edit, update and delete an existing record.
